snippet.description:
Who needs the Kwik-E-Mart? I do! You know how much I love teeny tiny details and this set is chockfull of them! In The Kwik-E-Mart 71017, the Simpsons nostalgia is high - gotta love all the hidden (and not so hidden) jokes. I though this would be a great introduction into the Simpsons Lego World before I build the Simpsons House and I hope the house is just as entertaining. As you will probably guess, this is a massive build, here is Part 1 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mv6elkxbza0

Visit The Kwik-E-Mart—Springfield’s favorite convenience store!

Welcome to The Kwik-E-Mart—your one-stop shop for convenience foods at inconvenient prices! This highly detailed and iconic LEGO® version of The Simpsons™ store is packed with more rich, colorful details than a Mr. Burns birthday cake has candles! Walk under the huge Kwik-E-Mart sign and join Homer, Marge and Bart as they browse the aisles filled with beauty products, diapers, dog food, pastries, fruits, vegetables and more—including Krusty-O’s and Chef Lonelyheart’s Soup for One. Then head over to the refrigerated cases where you’ll find Buzz Cola, chocolate milk, various other drinks and snacks… and frozen Jasper! There’s also a Buzz Cola soda fountain, juice dispensers, coffee machine, arcade games, ATM and stacks of Powersauce boxes. At the counter, Apu is ready to tempt you with a variety of printed magazines, comic books, cards, tofu hot dogs, freshly expired donuts and his ever-popular hallucination-inducing Squishees. At the back, there’s a storage closet complete with rat and an exit. On the roof you’ll discover Apu’s secret vegetable garden, while outside this amazing model features bright-yellow walls, 2 phone booths, a stack of purple crates, and a dumpster area with ‘El Barto’ graffiti, opening door and an iconic blue dumpster that also opens. You can also remove the roof and open out the rear walls for easy access. This set also includes Snake (a.k.a. Jailbird), who loves nothing more than stealing cars and robbing the Kwik-E-Mart—but this time Chief Wiggum is hot on his tail in his police car. Capture this bandit and return peace to the town of Springfield and the amazing Kwik-E-Mart. This fantastic set includes 6 minifigures with assorted accessory elements: Homer Simpson, Bart Simpson, Marge Simpson, Apu Nahasapeemapetilon, Chief Wiggum and Snake (a.k.a. Jailbird).

snippet.description:
Our magical sun gives gardens and farms the light and warmth they need to grow the ingredients that go into all our favourite foods. Kyra's unboxing the super fun Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz experiment kit to show you how food grows!

Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz: Grow Your Garden, Grow Your Learning

Plants are magic. They give us oxygen to breathe, and they give us delicious food and fruits to eat.

Kyra is learning the science behind the magic with the help of her new Garden Sciencz Experimental Educational Game by Piramal Healthcare's Jungle Magic series for kids. She has donned her lab coat, and her thinking cap as she learns step by step the processes that go into planting a seed, making it sprout and nurturing it into a fully grown plant.

What is more, now that Kyra knows how important different types of soil are she is also closely observing all the different muds of India wherever she goes, which means a lot more dirt on her hands and shoes! But her parents don't mind so much. She is getting closer to nature after all.  

The Garden Sciencz kit contains 20 different experiments in growing plants, soil samples, and different types of seeds of food crops like wheat, coriander, mustard, fenugreek and many more. Kyra is eagerly waiting for her "food to start growing" on her plants, she checks on them every five minutes! If you have a curious little person in your life, we suggest you get them this kit too to arouse some hunger for observing nature as well as appreciation for patient practice of gardening.

Suitable for ages 7 and above, this kit contains an instruction manual with an introduction to different Indian soils and crops and a detailed guide to growing plants. It contains everything the child will need to grow their own plant, except for water. All material used is environment friendly.

snippet.title: Lego Elves Fire Dragon's Lava Cave Set Build Review Play - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Oh! Do you hear that? It's the sound of my heart gushing over and falling head over heels in love with the Lego Elves Dragons! New releases for 2016 (and accompanied by the second Lego Elves mini-movie) is a wave of Lego Elves sets and they feature dragons. Dragons! I love these fantasy sets so very much. In this one, the friends Azari Firedancer the fire elf and Emily Jones meet Zonya the Fire Dragon and travel to her Fire Dragon's Lava Cave set 41175. There's much to love here, even after the dragon build, with a mossy lava cave and magical components and a new map for an important quest to save the Queen Dragon. There's a poisoned well and pink crystals and.... I think you're just going to have to watch for yourselves as I am too excited and have stopped being coherent. Let me know what you think!

Have a campfire at the Lava Cave with Zonya the fire dragon!

Join Emily Jones and Azari Firedancer the fire elf, as they explore the Lava Cave! Meet Zonya the fire dragon, then enter the Lava Cave with the use of Azari’s magic fire powers. Discover the secret map and roast a marshmallow around the campfire. Spend the night tucked into the warm and cozy moss beds in the cave, and in the morning join Emily and Azari on Zonya’s back for an epic flight!

Includes Emily Jones and Azari Firedancer mini-doll figures, plus Zonya the fire dragon.
Features the Lava Cave, with a sliding function to move the lava fall aside, moss beds and a campfire. Includes the Shadow Fountain with a sliding function to transform the fountain from green poisoned water to blue clean water.
Clean up Shadow Fountain so Zonya can drink from it once again.
Help Azari open the Lava Cave using the sliding function to move the lava fall to the side.
Set up camp, build a fire and roast a marshmallow.
Fly off on Zonya with Friends Emily and Azari for more adventures.
